### Edge Cases and Error Scenarios Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api

### Flight Edge Cases

### Test 1: Invalid price parameters (non-numeric)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?minPrice=abc&maxPrice=def

### Test 2: Negative price values
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?minPrice=-1000&maxPrice=-500

### Test 3: Min price higher than max price
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?minPrice=50000&maxPrice=10000

### Test 4: Invalid bundle type
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?bundle=premium

### Test 5: Invalid boolean for availableOnly
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?availableOnly=maybe

### Test 6: Invalid date format
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureDate=invalid-date

### Test 7: Future date that doesn't exist in data
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureDate=2026-01-01

### Test 8: Empty route parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route//

### Test 9: Single slash in route
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/BUD/

### Test 10: Very long station codes
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/VERYLONGCODE/ANOTHERLONGCODE

### Test 11: Special characters in station codes
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/BUD%20TEST/LTN%20TEST

### Station Edge Cases

### Test 12: Empty IATA parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?iata=

### Test 13: Very long IATA code
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?iata=VERYLONGIATACODE

### Test 14: Special characters in name search
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=London%20%26%20Paris

### Test 15: Empty name parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=

### Test 16: Single character name search
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=L

### Test 17: Numeric values in name search
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=123

### Test 18: Special characters in IATA lookup
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/BUD%20TEST

### Test 19: Very long station IATA in connections
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/VERYLONGIATACODE/connections

### Test 20: Empty search term
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/

### Test 21: Single character search
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/L

### Test 22: Search with special characters
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/London%20%26%20Airports

### Multiple Parameters Tests

### Test 23: All flight filters combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureStation=BUD&arrivalStation=LTN&departureDate=2025-07-09&bundle=basic&minPrice=10000&maxPrice=25000&availableOnly=true

### Test 24: All station filters combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?iata=BUD&name=Budapest&hasConnection=LTN

### Test 25: Conflicting parameters (should still work)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?iata=BUD&name=London

